ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project is a complete C# modernization of "The Millionaire Game" originally
created by Marco Loenen (Macronair) in VB.NET. While maintaining the core concept
and inspiration from the original, this version represents a substantial rewrite
with significant architectural improvements, new features, and enhanced capabilities
including:

- Complete migration to modern .NET 8.0 with C# 12
- Unified SQL Server database architecture
- Web-Based Audience Participation System (WAPS) with real-time SignalR communication
- Advanced audio system with DSP capabilities
- All six lifelines fully implemented
- Progressive Web App (PWA) for mobile participation
- And many other enhancements

Original VB.NET project: https://github.com/Macronair/TheMillionaireGame

Any derivative works, modifications, or distributions must include attribution to
both the original creator (Marco Loenen/Macronair) and the C# modernization developer
(Jean Francois Delgado) as specified in this license.
